}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "GL5254RT-2A2-B10 VER:T1.3" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. This is the same board ID as the [[D-Link DI-624 rev A1]].
The processor is assumed to be a VR4131.
The manual says the default SSIDs for both bands are '''default'''.
